@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_bdsgpk(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.exp((wp.exp(v2 + 0.62) - 0.71))
    tmp = tmp
    v0 = (wp.abs(wp.cos(v0 + 0.01)) * ((v2 + 0.10 + tmp + 0.82) * wp.cos(v0 + 0.60)))
    v2 = v0
    data[tid] = v0
